    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 6,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Eula_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "優菈",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "優菈的元素爆發在傷害倍率比例中佔比較高，以至於該武器的副詞綴對她來說不算特別劣勢，武器特效的真空刃也能夠享受物理傷害提高和敵人物抗降低帶來的提升，是優菈五星武器中的一種選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 48,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Razor_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "雷澤",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "雷澤輸出模式為元素爆發後使用普通攻擊進行輸出，非常適合該武器的特效。同時，該武器較高的基礎攻擊力能有效彌補雷澤基礎攻擊力較低的問題。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 11,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Beidou_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "北斗",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "北斗定位為副C時，開啟元素爆發後在後臺能為主C提供可觀的額外雷元素傷害，缺點是元素爆發需要能量很高。該武器在增加其全傷害的同時彌補了充能問題，是副C北斗的不錯選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 45,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Chongyun_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "重雲",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "重雲元素爆發需要能量較少，冷卻時間較短，可以頻繁觸發武器技能，但充能容易溢出，會因此浪費掉一些屬性，對重雲來說只能說是可用的武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 41,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xinyan_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "辛焱",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器能夠彌補辛焱基礎攻擊力較低的問題，同時提供一定的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "充能效率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，能夠一定程度上提高元素爆發的輸出量和釋放頻率。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
